# introduction 

Azure Synapse Analytics includes serverless SQL pools, which are tailored for querying data in a data lake

## Serverless SQL pools in Azure Synapse Analystics

Azure Synapse SQL is a distributed query system in Azure Synapse Analytics that offers two kinds of runtime environments:
  - Serverless SQL 
    - on-demand SQL query processing, primarily used to work with data in a data lake

  - dedicated SQL pool
    - Enterprise-scale relational database instances used to host data warehouse in which data is stored in relational tables.

